Package: mcpower
Title: Statistical Power Analysis via MCPower Engine
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R:
    person("Paweł", "Lenartowicz", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pawellenartowicz@europe.com")
Description: R bindings for the MCPower simulation engine. Provides OLS, GLM,
    mixed-effects, and ANOVA power analysis via a compiled Rust backend.
